# College Bumping Module (Phase 3+)

**Sector-optional** — only enabled when `UnionConfig.enabledModules` includes `"bumping"`.

## Access
- MFA required
- `stability_member` and `local_president` — full write
- `local_steward` — read committee only
- Hide module entirely for unions without college bumping needs

## PDF Handling
- Client-side parse where possible for privacy
- Server store + virus scan deferred to Phase 7 — memory adapter for MVP
- Decision log exportable for local records; included in hybrid slice (Phase 4)

## Disclaimer
Comparison checklists assist committee process — not legal advice.

See `docs/modules/COLLEGE_BUMPING.md`.

## Do Not
- Show bumping nav to non-college unions
- Mix grievance and bumping data access without separate permissions
- Auto-decide bumping outcomes in software
